Steps to generate CIX files from Ruby:

1. Download the source for the Ruby version to create a CIX for.
2. ./configure && make rdoc
3. Wait.
4. Come back to this directory and run
     ruby gen-from-ri-dir.rb --ri-dir=/path/to/ruby-X.Y/.ext/rdoc \
       --lib-dir=/path/to/ruby-X.Y/lib > ruby-X.Y.cix
